{"tid":398703,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！我隻貓係咪生癬？","createTime":"2017-09-13T11:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T17:51:49.000Z","uid":143817,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f08f72f00b7bec16124b6a4bc3a3cf069bb76b65","tid":398703,"uid":143817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"依幾日佢都係咁嗌<br />\n平時都唔係咁<br />\n直到今日仔細望先發覺佢背脊有個位無左d毛<br />\n有無人知咩事？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/192937_06f01dc30af317bf6ee1bb94c9ab68e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F192937_06f01dc30af317bf6ee1bb94c9ab68e7.jpg&h=283d3c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住依幾日都會帶佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea474fd6e4ccfa0010375ae3c4bb5311c72188f6","tid":398703,"uid":143817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0eba44e70619ca51581fb1dba0480251ff5224","tid":398703,"uid":53694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"皮膚病 快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"5d53c36a5e569156df791d8964373be9686de6af","tid":398703,"uid":143817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮膚病 快啲睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩幫左佢用消毒<br />\n我屋企最快都要幾日後先得閒帶到佢去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1a603c62c3cd75d5b80968b32d930750dea9b6","tid":398703,"uid":53694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"叫你啲朋友帶佢睇醫生先啦"},{"pid":"64eb056114f93355614477edd9263a9a24f1bd4a","tid":398703,"uid":143817,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你啲朋友帶佢睇醫生先啦</blockquote><br />\n我搽左娥羅納英落佢到  有無幫助？"},{"pid":"573000bb885060ef0550a6160f23b7d2d035cfba","tid":398703,"uid":64610